    - Sudan (VI-10)
    - Venezuela (VI-5)
* New entries:
    - Bonaire, Sint Eustatius and Saba (VI-8)
    - Cura√ßao (VI-8)
    - Sint Maarten (Dutch part) (VI-8)
    - South Sudan (VI-10)
